{"tid":2075456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動post][請置頂］工會平台發動聯署行動向G20國領事館請願","createTime":"2020-06-23T00:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T17:12:49.000Z","uid":194325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3cb9d65f783be3e8a1afd8c2973c80d6f4b097","tid":2075456,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T00:51:45.000Z","msg":"📜香港金總喺工會平台記者會提到今次G20行動會向國際發起聯署活動，收集會員聯署，向國際發聲！我哋好希望未加入工會嘅你唔好再猶疑！一齊把握最後發聲機會！☄️<br />\n<br />\n今次聯署活動只限工會會員，大家都以喺下面條 Link 到搵到聯署內容，俾大家做參考，希望大家踴躍發聲，爭取最後機會！<br />\n<br />\n🔖聯署內容：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c%2Fedit&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7h21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=3d6d1f7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n📥聯署 FAQ<br />\nQ1. 今次 &quot;G20 國集團領事館馬拉松式請願&quot; 有咩目的？<br />\nA1. G20國集團領事館馬拉松式請願係承接工會罷工公投後對抗極權嘅第二波反國安行動，目的係要顯示香港人對國安法嘅民意，請求G20國集團就香港保護自由民主運動提供實際支援。<br />\n<br />\nQ2. 點解要以民意爭取國際支援？<br />\nA2.  香港是國際都會，各國喺香港都有話語權同影響中國政府對香港打壓民主自由嘅能力。因此除香港人自身嘅努力外，國際實質支援都極為重要，絕對可以左右中共嘅決定。<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 點解要搞會員實名聯署呢？個人資料有冇被暴露風險？<br />\nA3. 基於坊間聯署大多匿名進行而欠公信力，而普通實名聯署有暴露個人私隱風險，參與工會現提供改善方案進行聯署。工會將負責核實聯署會員身份，以工會名義保證每一個簽名屬實，最後提交給領事館的聯署名單則為會員提供的化名保護會員身份。<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 點解要加入工會參加聯署呢？如果我未能參加工會又可唔可以參加聯署？<br />\nA4. 因為只有加入工會，工會才可擔保該會員身份屬實，而維持該聯署的公信力。如果你未能加入工會，亦可到參加請願行動的區議員辦事處或街站支持反國安匿名聯署。<br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n參加工會：<br />\n<br />\n- 香港金融業職工總會<br />\n- 香港會計手足工會<br />\n- 政府非公務員職工總會<br />\n- 香港貿易推銷及採購職工會<br />\n- 香港旅遊業革新總工會<br />\n- 香港資訊科技界工會<br />\n- 香港寵物界工會<br />\n- 社會及政治組織從業員工會<br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n#聯合工會 #pettition #聯署 #全民反國安 #還我真香港<br />\n#工會戰線 #國際戰線 #聯署 #AntiNationalSecurityLaw<br />\n#工會平台 #反國安法 #民意 <br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#記得緊貼我哋Channel <br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n📃入會申請表 Application Form📃<br />\n中文入會表：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XB1sA9TWEPY7ZEqq7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXB1sA9TWEPY7ZEqq7&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7h21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=74dd9897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XB1sA9TWEPY7ZEqq7</a><br />\nEng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/xTFeo7NLmENL6M6U8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FxTFeo7NLmENL6M6U8&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7h21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=dea44618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/xTFeo7NLmENL6M6U8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WJPDZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WJPDZc.jpg&h=7a53ad41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGss95T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGss95T.jpg&h=75448488&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36fb207bf7a64029798de4d1ade89a016a2ac20b","tid":2075456,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T00:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"f15442c1ab332434c787e9d0f61c6dadb40fbf4b","tid":2075456,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"要出動啦"},{"pid":"4f3fd5a83149615d54daeee83ba9d5ee197dc63e","tid":2075456,"uid":263018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T01:25:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38901fdbebb6fc32cd02033244d8239438bd623d","tid":2075456,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T01:26:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ffa343348259bcf5053cbe7f174850e13df4002d","tid":2075456,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T01:32:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e16d4b144fa496e6f856cab379407c0f547b13b0","tid":2075456,"uid":194325,"like":0,"di